    <h1> Chocolate Fudge </h1>
    <h2> Description <h2>
    <p> This chocolate fudge is absolutely delightful!</p>
    <p> The recipe below is guaranteed to give you satisfaction. </p>
    <h2> Ingredients </h2>
    <ul> 
      <li> chocolate </li>
      <li> salt </li>
      <li> vanilla </li>
      <li>Sweetened condensed milk </li>
    </ul>
    <h2> Steps </h2>
    <ol>
      <li> Step 1 Combine chocolate and condensed milk in a saucepan. </li>
      <li> Step 2 Remove from heat and pour into prepared pan. </li>
      <li> Step 3 Place into refrigerator for 1 hour, then remove them to cut in to squares.</li>
    </ol>
